<body class="index_html">

  <div class="nav_bar">
    <a href="/menu">
      <li class="bar_content">메뉴</li>
    </a>
    <a href="/write">
      <li class="bar_content">작성하기</li>
    </a>
    <a href="/check">
      <li class="bar_content">검사하기</li>
    </a>
  </div>

  <li class="tops__">
    <span class="gray">[ <%= post_types %> ],</span>
    <span class="orange"> <%= post_mbti %>,</span>
    <span class="black"> <%= user_name %> </span>
  </li>
  
  <li class="bordersf">
    <span class="grayi">
      <%= Number(times) - (Number(upload_time)) + 1 %>분 전
    </span>
  </li>

    <h1 class="top_list"><%= post_title %></h1>

    <textarea class="addr" readonly><%= post_description %></textarea>

    <br><br><br>

    <div class="ccc">
      <button class=" ud" data-id="<%= _id %>" onclick="ddel()"> 삭제하기 </button>
    </div>

      <script>
        var txtArea = $(".addr");
        var a = 400;
        if (txtArea) {
          txtArea.each(function () {
            a += 1;
            $(this).height(this.scrollHeight + a);
          });
        }

        a = 0;
      </script>

    </div>

      <br>

      <div class="modals_out">
        <div class="modals">
          확인을 누르시면 글이 삭제됩니다. <br>
          삭제된 글은 복구가 불가능합니다. <br>
          글 작성시 입력한 비밀번호를 적어주세요.
          <input type="password" class="pwpw" maxlength="6">
          <button class="btns" data-id="<%= _id %>"> 확인 </button>
          <div class="gray" onclick="nono()">삭제 안 할래요</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <script>
        function ddel() {
          document.querySelector('.modals_out').style.display = 'block'
          }

          function nono() {
            document.querySelector('.modals_out').style.display = 'none'
          }
      </script>

      <style>

          input[type=password] {
            letter-spacing: 8.5px;
          }

          .btns {
            background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);
            border: 1px solid gray;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 80px;
          }

          input:focus {
            outline: none;
          }

          .pwpw {
            width: 50%;
            margin: 20px;
            margin-left: 0;
            padding: 9px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            border: 1px solid gray;
            border-radius: 15px;
          }

        div {
          box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .modals {
           width: 100%;
           background: white;
           padding: 20px;
           font-size: 13px;
           line-height: 35px;
           border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .modals_out {
          width: 100%;
          height: 300px;
          background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
          position: absolute;
          padding: 20px;
          display: none
        }
      </style>

      <script>

        $('.btns').click(function(event_) {
          var pwisit = $('.pwpw').val();
          var 글번호 = event_.target.dataset.id; 
          var 지금누른거 = $(this);

          $.ajax({
            method: 'DELETE',
            url: '/editordelete',
            data: {
              _id: 글번호,
              pwisit: pwisit
            },
          })
          .done((result) => {
            alert('삭제되었습니다.');
            location.href = '/'
          })
          .fail(function(xhr, textStatus, errorThrown) {
            alert('비밀번호를 잘못 입력하셨습니다.')
            console.log(xhr, textStatus, errorThrown)
          })
        });

      </script>

  </div>

  <div id="footer">
    Developer: LEE HARAM / Contant: slyram06@icloud.com
